{"tid":1473644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太和街坊CCTV揭警講大話","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:06:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"18fe4d73e42dfcee9f8839f07ed34f78e767eed4","tid":1473644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190815/20749436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749436&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=d0991c6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749436&h=16fefa23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190815/20749436</a><br />\n<br />\n太和街坊CCTV揭警講大話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190815/large/1565801902_3428.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190815%2Flarge%2F1565801902_3428.gif&h=54fa8e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n監察組片段顯示，沒有任何人不斷開關升降機門妨礙警察上樓。閉路電視畫面<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】周二警方記者會上，公共關係科總警司謝振中指摘市民對警方「有情緒」，其間更播片指周日在大埔太和邨處理一宗自殺案時，被居民質疑為何警察可進入屋苑，並稱警車被包圍。「太和邨法團監察組」在fb專頁公開閉路電視片段，指事發時「未見警方稱『不斷開關升降機門妨礙警察上樓』的街坊」，又指是「便衣警員不願登記」，街坊才憤而尾隨至警車，而非「包圍警車」，直斥警方「斷章取義，用一小段影片欺瞞香港市民，指太和街坊妨礙救援工作，嚴重影響太和邨街坊聲譽」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥惡意抹黑強加罪名<br />\n<br />\n監察組前晚上載片段，帖文指已「取得太和業主立案法團同意，嘗試利用閉路電視還原真相」。片中可見，五名軍裝警員及一名便衣當晚10時30分進入麗和樓，保安員只詢問目的地，亦沒有街坊阻撓。15分鐘後，其中三名警員與隨行的保安主管由高樓層乘升降機到大堂，再向高樓層出發，亦沒有任何人「不斷開關升降機門妨礙警察上樓」。<br />\n<br />\n到晚上11時03分，「由於離開前警察不願意向保安登記，引起街坊不忿，所以現場街坊要求警員出示委任證並登記，當時並未有任何妨礙離開」。區議員周炫瑋當時亦有向警員查詢，但「警員以太嘈為由，不顧而去，（太和邨）街坊並未有妨礙任何警員工作的行動」。監察組強調，太和邨街坊尊重警方工作，「但對於街坊被惡意抹黑，胡亂強加罪名，絕不啞忍」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳曉峰  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n催淚彈狂射無示威者民居<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n天水圍煙花襲擊 三男被捕"},{"pid":"980679b4b84e18aa5277836436b7b96e8d0ec8c1","tid":1473644,"uid":20119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"433832390a0adbfd31f1dfdc3e252d1a77ff56be","tid":1473644,"uid":40940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠人民公敵"},{"pid":"438a5610f776281bec487d7b0887351e45cfc1fe","tid":1473644,"uid":85694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"推到上4點鐘許sir節目"},{"pid":"b1c1670be318c391e36ea989923fcd4554afb48b","tid":1473644,"uid":99904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a666837c1b9f2fcc0e22dce43568310ffc136a3c","tid":1473644,"uid":37668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8625843c11b0a80d29317f1bf80057c6fc7c6b","tid":1473644,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cb8e83c06487d9af7f4e1dd23aa9aab6d304f18","tid":1473644,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"各位記者朋友你地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f499acab8f5f7e7858afd549515a9f57631b9460","tid":1473644,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"各位記者朋友你地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84ce3793e50ae114171dc3a51de4c02ff157b90","tid":1473644,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"各位記者朋友你地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd69cb2c89eada81f7af88c0ecf8a61e374966b3","tid":1473644,"uid":8